description: Nothing compares to an authentic Chicago style hot dog, and Papa George is sure the fine folks of Kentucky will agree! Chicago born and raised, Papa George knows his way around a hot dog cart, and he's ready and waiting to teach your taste buds how amazing a hot dog can be. Grab yourself a Brat, Polish Sausage, Italian Beef Sandwich, or the classic Chicago Dog today, and find out why everyone's talking about Papa George's Chicago Style Hot Dogs!
name: Papa George's Chicago Style Hot Dogs
